# normal

**Type Property**

Normal window level.

## Declaration

```swift
static var normal: WindowLevel { get }
```

## Discussion

Use this if you want your scene to have the normal window level instead of the level computed by [doc://com.apple.SwiftUI/documentation/SwiftUI/WindowLevel/automatic].
